ua.pp.ihorzak.alog

Interface ALogFormatterDelegate<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Class of instances which can be transformed to logging string using this class instances.

    public interface ALogFormatterDelegate<T>
    ALogFormatter delegate that is responsible for custom specified class instances transformation to string for logging. Should be used for ALogFormatter creation via ALogFormatter.create(ALogFormatterDelegate).
